(5017, 10, '_we_are_ready_headind', 'field_5d2701b1528e5'),
(5018, 10, 'we_are_ready_text', 'Instead of worrying about cleaning the commercial property, leave it to our commercial cleaning Geelong. Our cleaning experts ensure that you do not have to be stress about making each part of your commercial space spotless and shine. We remove scuff marks from walls and baseboards, vacuum the carpets, and wash the floors. We will remove dust, cobwebs, and other dirt and make your commercial space user-friendly.\r\nUpholstered chairs are particularly prone to accumulate dirt. It will also make the office look grimy and untidy. Our commercial cleaning gives all your furniture a thorough clean, creating a far more pleasant working environment. All types of flooring are prone to ‘wear and tear’ over time. It is a natural process due to heavy traffic and continual footfall. We never left any scratches, scuffs, and marks that ultimately make an excellent impression on visiting clients.'),
(5019, 10, '_we_are_ready_text', 'field_5d2701da528e6'),
