(5024, 10, 'next_week_text', 'Hiring our professional commercial cleaning for your organization is the best option. We will take good care of your office space from its floor and washroom. Along with that we also suggest a few good habits and some easy follow tricks that employees can follow to make their area clean. It will also contribute great support to our commercial cleaning service. Some valuable tips about our commercial cleaning in Geelong are as follows.\r\nBefore starting work, take a look at your work area and de-clutter if there are waste papers around your desk.\r\nEncourage employees to keep their desk clean by organizing their files, folders, and other items.\r\nKeep your wastebasket clean so that it does not attract bugs.\r\nPromote the employees to get their work desk organized to stay on the top of their job\r\nSort paperwork into piles, documents to be filed and archived,'),
