(809, 1, '2019-07-12 07:22:55', '2019-07-12 07:22:55', 'Nobody likes a messy or cluttered workplace. Since most employees spending more than one-third of the year at work, it is vital to maintain its cleanliness. It is the business owner responsibility to give their staff a clean, positive, and hygienic work environment. Our<strong><a href=\"https://cleaningcontractorsgeelong.com.au/industrial-cleaning/\">commercial cleaning in Geelong</a></strong> ultimately helps you for more productivity and business success.  Our specialized service will come in and treat the floor, and restore it to its former glory.\r\n\r\nCommercial cleaning may vary depending on the costs and the quality of work. Our specialized and skilled cleaners use the most modern equipment, and eco-friendly supplies to clean your office faster and better than our competitors. Before taking up the commercial cleaning task, we create a well-defined checklist that helps you get an excellent job done on time. It ensures all the areas of your office that need cleaning, including reception, conference room, workstations, desks, kitchen, washrooms, etc will became spot less. Ultimately we help you reduce the chances of mistakes and save your precious time.\r\n\r\nInstead of worrying about cleaning the commercial property, leave it to our commercial cleaning Geelong.  Our cleaning experts ensure that you do not have to be stress about making each part of your commercial space spotless and shine. We remove scuff marks from walls and baseboards, vacuum the carpets, and wash the floors.  We will remove dust, cobwebs, and other dirt and make your commercial space user-friendly.\r\n\r\nUpholstered chairs are particularly prone to accumulate dirt. It will also make the office look grimy and untidy. Our commercial cleaning gives all your furniture a thorough clean, creating a far more pleasant working environment. All types of flooring are prone to ‘wear and tear’ over time. It is a natural process due to heavy traff